# Page Divider 1988 - Privacy Policy

**Last Updated:** 07/29/2025

Thank you for using Page Divider 1988! This privacy policy explains how we handle your information.

## Data Collection
We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data, browsing history, or website content. The extension operates entirely locally within your browser.

## Storage Usage
The extension uses Chrome's storage API to remember your preferences (button position, colors, sizes) only on your device. These settings are never transmitted to any server.

## Permissions Justification
- **activeTab:** Required to inject controls only in your current tab when you activate the extension
- **scripting:** Used to add navigation buttons to web pages
- **storage:** Saves your customization preferences locally

## No Tracking
The extension contains no analytics, tracking codes, or data collection mechanisms. We have no servers to send data to.

## Changes to This Policy
Any updates to this policy will be posted on this page. For questions, contact us at [your-email@domain.com].
